title: Front Corner One Bedroom at The Princeton Hall Apartments
posting_body: ['Property Address', '888 Grand Ave - 306(1/2R) | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Front Corner One Bedroom at The Princeton Hall Apartments', 'This top-floor front corner one-bedroom apartment features a wonderful view of Grand Avenue.', 'It has classic hardwood floors throughout, northwest-facing windows, and updated lighting.', 'The kitchen features original built-in cabinets, full-size appliances, and a large dining area.', 'Located in the exciting Victoria Crossing stretch of Grand Avenue, the Princeton Hall Apartments are the perfect apartment for anyone who wants to experience the best of Grand living!', "You will always find something great to do with restaurants like the Cafe Latte, Billy's on Grand, Salut, and many more as well as tons of shopping locations, theaters, and other entertainment just outside your door.", 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Heat Paid', 'Water Paid', 'Controlled Entry', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Nine Foot Ceilings', 'On-Site Laundry Room', 'Separate Kitchen and Dining', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 750', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,045.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
